{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3711a76090","title":"林彪关于办好《解放军报》的指示","origin":"《林彪元帅文集》（下册），香港凤凰书品， 2016年。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"56efd6cd2d","index":0,"year":1960,"month":12,"day":null,"articleId":"3711a76090"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"33772fc88b","type":"title","text":"林彪关于办好《解放军报》的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3711a76090"},{"id":"69088ea44f","type":"paragraph","text":"高级领导机关办好报纸非常重要。要使报纸起宣传者和组织者的作用。报纸是高级领导机关实施领导的重要工具之一。因此，办好报纸是极端重要的事情。","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3711a76090"},{"id":"96e6a28072","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3711a76090"},{"id":"99dbda7c02","type":"paragraph","text":"要加强《解放军报》的思想性和现实性。思想性，就是旗帜鲜明，方向正确，高举毛泽东思想伟大的红旗，按照党中央、毛主席指示的精神办报；现实性，就是要反映部队的思想动态和部队的现实活动，主要是思想动态。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3711a76090"}],"page":{"id":"6fd646c30f","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"3711a76090","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}